下去，美国政府近年开始担心，可能再也无法阻止大陆通过武力解决台湾问题。美国印太司令部司令菲利普·戴维森在今年3月时曾在美国国会表示，中国大陆最快2027年就会武力解决台湾问题。如果这场冲突发生，将会是一场灾难。 文章解释，这场冲突不仅会导致两个核大国之间冲突的风险提升，而且会对全球经济造成影响。台湾的台积电公司是世界上重要的芯片制造商，世界上84%最先进的芯片都产自这里，如果台海冲突，台积电将受到影响，一旦停产恐导致全球电子业发展停滞。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IypTF65nv3tgLEAMaCDYzODkzNTg4IO2FroQGMAo4twJAGnIJNDU3MjYwNzU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"183 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-58de12349d477dfb16cd063649c125ad_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1619784649.7884283","card_id":"Q_457234462","target":{"id":457234462,"title":"如何看待网友反馈四川航空「五一」航班遭大面积取消，川航回应与事实不符，今日航班均正常运行？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/457234462","type":"question","created":1619743393,"answer_count":36,"follower_count":220,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[444,1740,3087,5582,216534],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"今日早间，有不少网友在社交平台反映，收到四川航空的航班取消短信，涉及航班包括长沙、成都、南京等多个航段。四川航空上午回应，与事实不符的航班取消短信，目前，公司正展开调查。众多旅客临时收到航班取消短信 四川航空：航班正常，原因正在调查"},"attached_info":"Cj8IypTF65nv3tgLEAMaCDYzODg3NzM2IKGlrYQGMAE43AFAG3IJNDU3MjM0NDYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"178 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-1acd5382b6837f93fba34539fa8015f8_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1619784649.7890415","card_id":"Q_456331604","target":{"id":456331604,"title":"你认为《火影忍者》中干架最多且最具含金量的是谁？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/456331604","type":"question","created":1619260540,"answer_count":43,"follower_count":189,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[43691,277123,392172],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"C